creator: Slide.buzz
descriptionHtml:
Slide is a Social Experience application that lets friends and families create social experiences and save those memories.

Social experiences could be visiting a bar with your friends, having your nails done, hanging out with your kids, their friends and their parents, brunch/dinner, parachute jump, happy hours, a weekend away or a trip around the world.

The ability to look back on those social experiences are core to our soul.
descriptionShort: We live for Experiences

title: Slide.travel

creator: Slide.buzz
descriptionHtml:
Travelling like a local gives you the benefit of a culturally immersive and authentic experience. It also builds respect for different cultures and global kinship.

Slide lets people share their favourite places to hangout, bars, restaurants, coffee shops, parks etc via a one minute or less video.

So our users get tips and suggestions from places like Nairobi, Amsterdam, Caracas and many other places.

Check out what people do for fun around the world and share with the world what you do for fun.

Let’s make it a smaller world.

You can find our Terms of Use Here: https://slide.travel/termsofservice

If you have any questions or need help, Please contact us at mazy@slide.travel

You can review more privacy related information at: https://slide.travel/privacy-policy

title: Slide.travel

creator: Slide.travel
descriptionHtml:
Save trip ideas as you research: Save links, pins, images, videos, events into a shared trip for your group. Keep all your trip ideas in one place.

Discover things to do: Slide's technology finds events, activities and dining for your group on your trip.

Plan with fellow travelers: Invite fellow travelers to add ideas to your trip. These things to do can be posted onto a calendar.

Store reservations: Slide will add your reservations to your trip in seconds. Simply forward your confirmation emails to an email we provide you, we will take it from there.


You can find our Terms of Use Here: https://slide.travel/termsofservice

If you have any questions or need help, Please contact us at mazy@slide.travel

You can review more privacy related information at: https://slide.travel/privacy-policy

Save trip ideas as you research: Save links, pins, images, videos, events into a shared trip for your group. Keep all your trip ideas in one place.

Discover things to do: Slide's technology finds events, activities and dining for your group on your trip.

Plan with fellow travelers: Invite fellow travelers to add ideas to your trip. These things to do can be posted onto a calendar.

Store reservations: Slide will add your reservations to your trip in seconds. Simply forward your confirmation emails to an email we provide you, we will take it from there.


You can find our Terms of Use Here: https://slide.travel/termsofservice

If you have any questions or need help, Please contact us at mazy@slide.travel

You can review more privacy related information at: https://slide.travel/privacy-policy
